Introduction

Burvey is a kid girl group under Kids Planet (On1 Entertainment and 4D Label) that debuted on May 1, 2020, with the song “Swing Bebe." The members are also models under 'Kipop'.

In November 2021, the members Seoyeon and Jiwoo left the group. In the first half of 2022, Yerin also left the group. On June 3, 2022, Yooran, Zia, and Seoyoon were added to Burvey.
